The true light that gives light to everyone was coming into the world.

35:29.019 --> 35:36.731
Jesus was in the world, and though the world was made through Jesus, the world did not recognize Jesus.

35:37.832 --> 35:42.980
Jesus came to that which were His own, and His own did not receive Jesus.

35:44.061 --> 35:52.594
Yet to all who do receive Jesus, to those who believe in Jesus' name, He gives the right to become children of God.

35:53.570 --> 35:59.558
Children not born of natural descent or human decision or husband's will, born of God.

36:00.720 --> 36:05.025
The word became flesh and made his dwelling among us.

36:05.246 --> 36:13.517
We have seen his glory, the glory of the one and only son who came from the father full of grace and truth.

36:14.618 --> 36:23.410
No one has ever seen God, but the one and only son who is himself God and his in closest relationship with the father has

36:23.618 --> 36:25.262
made Him known.

36:27.526 --> 36:28.849
This is what we confess is true.

36:28.869 --> 36:30.793
This is our hope.

36:31.856 --> 36:33.018
This is our faith.

36:34.601 --> 36:39.191
And this secures eternal life for us all who believe in Him.

36:40.073 --> 36:42.278
We do declare this in Jesus' name and we all say together.

36:42.298 --> 36:44.242
Amen.

